{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4a579c9840","title":"周恩来接见外交部各组织代表的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"061b6ad4be","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":1,"articleId":"4a579c9840","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"王海蓉","id":"0f1e109155","type":"人物"},{"name":"陈毅","id":"1feb996ca7","type":"人物"},{"name":"对外关系和政策","id":"2bffb53b5b","type":"主题"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"清查五·一六","id":"a0d5508956","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"288ea3c16c","type":"title","text":"周恩来接见外交部各组织代表的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a579c9840","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a9b0c34afc","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月一日，总理接见了外交部各组织的代表。参加接见的有陈毅及其他部党委成员，刘晓未参加。接见情况如下：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a579c9840","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9aa0970f85","type":"paragraph","text":"1、使馆在十二月份要立即办毛泽东思想学习班；","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a579c9840","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a9beafaca8","type":"paragraph","text":"2、对外交部东方红兵团（67.11.30成立的，属“外联”34战斗队一派）没表态，总理说：“东方红兵团声明很弱，政治主张不明确。”","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a579c9840","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2f16c62f01","type":"paragraph","text":"3、对“外联”34战斗队没表态。34战斗队代表曾发表意见，但被到会代表压了下去。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a579c9840","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e06136c2b3","type":"paragraph","text":"4、总理说：“业务监督小组暂时不要动，同志们要负起责任来，加强自信，把工作搞好。大联筹对他们的态度是正确的（指没有撤换监督人员）要斗私批修，学毛选。正确对待34个战斗队的群众。”","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a579c9840","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f72fe4d640","type":"paragraph","text":"5、总理说：“对516不要认为中共中央非常委员会有线索就认为没事了，还是有坏人的，要注意阶级斗争。”外交部自王焕德揪出后，又搞出了个泄密小集团。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a579c9840","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c75601757c","type":"paragraph","text":"6、总理还批评陈毅说：“你在北戴河会议上反王稼祥的“三和一少”是好的，但到广州会议就变了。”","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a579c9840","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"66dab89369","type":"paragraph","text":"参加接见的还有王海蓉、唐闻生（唐明照的女儿）","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a579c9840","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"63a22b17af","type":"paragraph","text":"（据外交口同志传达，非记录，供参考）","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4a579c9840","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}